InventoryItems.Name: Badminton Racket and Birdie
InventoryItems.Description: Affordable equipment for a kid-fun outdoor game! Kids will have hours of fun with this classic racquet game — great for day care centers, summer camps, vacation bible schools, recreation centers, family reunions, and so much more. Includes 25" full-size badminton racket with one birdie, assorted among a variety of bright colors. Ages 8+.
